author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Paychex Inc Posts Q3 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $0.63
text:
March 26 (Reuters) - Paychex Inc:
* Q3 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.72 * Q3 REVENUE $866.5 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $854.5 MILLION
* Q3 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.65 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* SEES 2018 TOTAL REVENUE IS EXPECTED TO GROW APPROXIMATELY 7%
* SEES 2018 INVESTMENT INCOME, NET IS EXPECTED TO BE APPROXIMATELY $8.0 MILLION
* SEES 2018 DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE IS EXPECTED TO INCREASE IN RANGE OF 13% TO 14%
* SEES 2018 ADJUSTED DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE IS EXPECTED TO INCREASE IN RANGE OF 15% TO 16%
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.53, REVENUE VIEW $3.36 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
